<span class="large" style="margin-bottom: 20px; z-index: 2; position: fixed">
  Kai Cooper &nbsp; .small.highlight[**Wharton**]<br>
  Gregory Lanzalotto &nbsp; .small.highlight[**Wharton**]<br>
